This new set stars the most amazing new grappler to appear in years, 2003 Abu Dhabi World Champion, Marcelo Garcia. What you will learn on these tapes is that Marcelo Garcia?s techniques are not based on size, strength or superior conditioning. His moves are so unique that most of his opponents are unsure of that to do when fighting him. What Marcelo teaches is the exact strategies and techniques he used to win the 2003 Submission Grappling World Championships.

Prepare to have your guard game changed forever! Marcelo Garcia?s guard is the most talked about grappling game in years. His performance in the World Championships has virtually re-wrote what can be done from your back in a fight. Marcelo Garcia?s new X-Guard is the most effective and powerful guard position since the Spider guard and this video has it all!
